### **1. Smart Farming Drone ‚Äì PEAS Representation**

| **Component**           | **Description**                                                                          |
| ----------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Performance Measure** | Crop health monitoring accuracy, pesticide usage efficiency, area coverage, battery life |
| **Environment**         | Farmland, crops, pests, weather, flying conditions                                       |
| **Actuators**           | Propellers, pesticide sprayer, camera gimbal                                             |
| **Sensors**             | Camera (multispectral or infrared), GPS, wind speed sensor, altimeter                    |

üìù **Use Case**: Crop monitoring, disease detection, and precision spraying.

---

### **2. AI Music Composer ‚Äì PEAS Representation**

| **Component**           | **Description**                                                             |
| ----------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Performance Measure** | Melody originality, harmony quality, listener satisfaction, genre adherence |
| **Environment**         | Musical data, genres, instruments, user preferences                         |
| **Actuators**           | Audio output system, digital instruments, music file generator              |
| **Sensors**             | User input, style/genre selection, mood detection from user behavior        |

üìù **Use Case**: Composing background scores, personalized playlists, or AI-generated songs.

---

### **3. AI-Based Mental Health Chatbot ‚Äì PEAS Representation**

| **Component**           | **Description**                                                                     |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Performance Measure** | User satisfaction, emotional support success, accuracy of responses, session length |
| **Environment**         | Conversations, emotional states, context history                                    |
| **Actuators**           | Text generator, voice output (optional), sentiment-based response selector          |
| **Sensors**             | Text input, voice tone analyzer (if available), sentiment analysis engine           |

üìù **Use Case**: Offering emotional support, stress reduction, and mental health check-ins.
